# Department and User Management System

This is a Java-based Department and User Management System built using the MVC architecture. It allows role-based access to manage users, roles, and departments. Data is stored using simple `.txt` files for easy file-based persistence.

## ğŸš€ Features

* User and Role Management
* Department Management
* File-based Data Persistence
* Role-based Access Control
* Modular Code for Easy Collaboration

